<font color="#006400" size="+2"><a name="bio">Biographical</a></font>
</p>

<blockquote>
<table>
<tr>
    <td>Name:</td>    
    <td>Hilary MANTEL</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td>Nationality:</td>
    <td>England</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td>Born:</td>    
    <td>6 July 1952</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td>Awards:</td>
    <td><font size="-1">Shiva Naipaul Memorial Prize, 1987</font></td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td></td>
    <td><font size="-1">Winifred Holtby Award, 1990</font></td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td></td>
    <td><font size="-1">Hawthornden Prize, 1996</font></td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td></td>
    <td><font size="-1"><a href="http://www.themanbookerprize.com/interview/man-booker-prize-2009-winner-hilary-mantel" target="_blank">Man Booker Prize, 2009</a></font></td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td></td>
    <td><font size="-1"><a href="http://www.themanbookerprize.com/news/hilary-mantel-wins-2012-man-booker-prize" target="_blank">Man Booker Przie, 2012</a></font></td>
</tr>
</table>
<br>

<font size="-1">
<ul>
	<li>Born in Derbyshire, England
	<li>Attended LSE and University of Sheffield
	<li>Lived in Botswana (1977-1982) and Saudi Arabia (1983-1986)
</ul>
</font>

</blockquote>

